Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.36,0:00:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.08,0:00:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.96,0:00:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.24,0:00:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.33,0:01:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.30,0:01:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.96,0:01:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.63,0:01:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去喝酒了是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,喝了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人實在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.95,0:02:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我道歉有什麼用?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你自己的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天起有重要的畢業考不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然還有心情去喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.56,0:02:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,那是情勢所逼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.67,0:02:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論你會不會畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.47,0:02:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論你能不能當上褓父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實這種事,我都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.51,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能全力以赴\N去做你決定的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣就是最好的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不管你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想大學畢業的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就再稍微認真用功一下如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.45,0:03:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#86衝擊的一夜!\N明日菜的莎拉紀念日?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡睡著的話\N對身體不太好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.40,0:03:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳才是呢\N妳跑來這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.64,0:03:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又還沒有訂婚\N應該還只是外人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.75,0:03:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一傳出什麼奇怪的傳聞\N妳該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.33,0:03:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於訂婚的事\N我想跟你談一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.64,0:04:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\N我不太清楚訂婚究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳去問我叔叔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我一直都是\N這門親事的局外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.52,0:04:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然不知道訂婚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,事到如今…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.34,0:04:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N我會請我爸媽取消婚約的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取消婚約吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.95,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我已經知道你真正的心意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解…解脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.43,0:05:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的主人,真是個好女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.06,0:06:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,我把莎拉放在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.35,0:07:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生,醒一醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三…三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.41,0:08:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去了,莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐,請您儘管放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.74,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上的事\N我不會告訴老爺和夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.68,0:08:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早餐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰做的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,昨天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那麼大家一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱五代明年\N會有更好的成績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.72,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.02,0:09:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼一副無精打采的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能跟管理員有關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也沒有出來送五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的眼睛紅紅的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.94,0:10:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚五代好像沒怎麼睡\N是不是啊,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.37,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道,我睡得很熟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打了他一巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他喝酒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我狠狠打了他一巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.79,0:10:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳不用在意\N是裕作自己不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,誰叫他喝酒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.73,0:10:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這麼一來\N五代肯定畢不了業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.97,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,五代根本不值得同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是畢不了業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的囉\N被管理員打了一巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神上一定受到很大的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你自己的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想大學畢業的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就再稍微認真用功一下如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.18,0:12:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在等五代回來啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.99,0:12:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能又跑去哪裡喝酒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧,明天還要繼續考試耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是逃跑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.04,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,這位老闆\N現在超低價時段哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,別跑啊,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.61,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,景氣真差啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.38,0:12:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,五代\N你不是請了溫書假嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,不過有點狀況…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.24,0:12:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們很想我嗎?\N我馬上就能回來陪你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,陪我玩積木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,唸故事書給我聽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.88,0:13:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,我一定要畢業\N然後當上褓父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果他昨晚沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會去參加畢業考嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.31,0:13:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦\N都被管理員打了一巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.88,0:13:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代失去奮鬥的目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.85,0:13:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,五代是為了妳\N才想畢業當上褓父的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種選擇職業的方法\N未免太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.36,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是這種男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有骨氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是有沒有骨氣的問題…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.30,0:14:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人在偷看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?你去參加畢業考了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.99,0:14:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天只有考上午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你昨晚睡在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡在酒家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.43,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上我一個人想了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美\N那個魷魚乾是我想吃的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛那麼小氣啊,章魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.34,0:14:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是花枝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們有沒有在聽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係\N反正回來就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,為了慶祝五代平安回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.75,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是要“回來”這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我暫時不會回來一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想以最佳的狀態去考畢業考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以從今天起\N我要住在酒家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這裡也是最佳住處啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且有酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.54,0:15:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了\N我偶爾會回來拿換洗衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,畢業考好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.19,0:15:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,人活著坦率最重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉強的話,都不會有什麼好下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.42,0:16:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎\N千萬不要再勉強自己哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你好好加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜留下這封信走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留書出走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道她失蹤了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.98,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,她是去伊豆的別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.12,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那我先看看這封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.53,0:16:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生和我\N我們的心情都還沒有整理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就訂婚\N我覺得時間有點早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請將訂婚的日子延期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.48,0:16:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,延期?我記得昨天晚上她說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會請我爸媽取消婚約的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.12,0:17:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果變成延期,意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問發生了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.86,0:17:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,沒有,沒有什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.40,0:17:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,我想盡快和明日菜小姐\N兩人單獨談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.01,0:17:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有勸過她了,可是她不肯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚後來的事情\N我怎麼都想不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成那樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道,在那之後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很有可能會做出那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:18:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是萬一做了的話\N我應該勇敢的負起責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.36,0:18:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在九條家\N已經當了20年的司機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.23,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從明日菜小姐還是嬰兒的時候\N一直做到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.31,0:18:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她從小就很坦率誠懇\N是個非常善良的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的事也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.28,0:18:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為大小姐是為了袒護你\N把一切都藏在心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.13,0:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.34,0:19:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你正在考畢業考,不是嗎?\N幹嘛來住這種地方呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁我的決心還沒鬆動之前\N想好好拼一拼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.58,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了某人下定決心\N一定要畢業當上褓父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.45,0:19:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果她不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.15,0:19:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果我畢不了業\N連工作也放棄的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.96,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我自己的存在價值\N究竟在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想先一個人努力看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.47,0:19:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己無法做到\N哪有資格去照顧別人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.44,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的說,是你被你馬子甩了\N還是說你逃了出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪一種?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.61,0:19:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這種事情啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是逃出來的話\N絕對不可以回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.95,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,一定要堅持到她道歉為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.66,0:19:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男女之間啊\N追的那一方才是輸家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要拼命的逃\N不斷的逃,跑給她追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.89,0:20:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一她不追過來的話\N怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!那時候就要乖乖放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用最快的速度趕回去\N向她下跪道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人是很單純的\N他們吃這一套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.46,0:20:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是逃出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.49,0:20:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想暫時自己努力看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.47,0:20:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力試著忘了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.74,0:20:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在,我相信我辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.48,0:21:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐,對不起\N我無法等到妳回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.63,0:21:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,那頓早餐很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…總而言之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.11,0:21:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天一整個晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳都在我的房裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.82,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.48,0:22:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有沒有做出什麼失禮的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.62,0:22:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.36,0:22:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-請問…\N-什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.97,0:22:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,也並不是全都不記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.74,0:22:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記的,因為我是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.52,0:22:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,請你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會逼你娶我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.79,0:22:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會追來這裡找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.53,0:22:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.51,0:23:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟他還是學生嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪他會累成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.26,0:23:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,想了的話我就輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.03,0:23:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能想響子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.36,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.37,0:23:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.74,0:23:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是他的馬子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼下定決心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.34,0:23:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來可能撐不了幾天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.95,0:23:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.79,0:23:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜…她懷孕了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.90,0:23:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,是三鷹教練的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.50,0:23:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是令人大吃一驚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.30,0:24:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎,這是理所當然的結果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.97,0:24:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.57,0:24:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『明日菜懷孕?\N三鷹驚人的結婚宣言!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.95,0:24:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.62,0:24:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.79,0:24:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.83,0:24:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.10,0:24:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.17,0:24:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.91,0:24:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.62,0:24:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.45,0:24:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.66,0:25:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.54,0:25:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.45,0:25:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.08,0:25:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.32,0:25:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.69,0:25:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
